{"tid":1911814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又係黃衛兵？又一間黃店即將收皮","createTime":"2020-03-05T15:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T15:19:41.000Z","uid":43066,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13d97b3c171d23510a262be75c3944f5c7bb4c45","tid":1911814,"uid":43066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"先前推飲食係有回響，攪攪下出現左好多黃衛兵又話貼幾塊野唔夠又話無捐錢點點點，你做撚過生意未？要顧慮好多野架，經濟圈概念大家忘記哂？定淨係得飲食？<br />\n<br />\n係咪間間要渣哥同龍門咁出位先得？飲食可能幫到手既，野日日都要食幾十蚊餐大部人負擔到，但市面上重有好多行業需要大家支持，唔係叫你地買d唔鐘意既野，有需要咪去左先囉，好撚過去doublepark啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔真係登死好多人，做生意下下跟到你個bid 咩，又要指定捐乜又要人地夢遊，有派野又攪年宵又請手足就業撐本地brand重想點？好多野係要形成唔係批鬥，家下比popo點埋相，有幾次夢遊行過見到有人屌佢地扮黃抽水真係想屌撚哂你老母。 岩岩睇到蝕緊錢都要捐真係忍唔住屌你班黃衛兵，自己了解下啦等陣又話我打手，係咪要執9哂先開心<br />\n<br />\n白粉報導<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200217/bkn-20200217050013479-0217_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200217%2Fbkn-20200217050013479-0217_00822_001.html&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaqzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=2a51c5f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200217/bkn-20200217050013479-0217_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家要倒貼差唔多10萬，如果情況持續，可能做多半年都做唔住！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZfraoF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZfraoF.png&h=f46c339d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4B2tam.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4B2tam.png&h=65df48d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"059d7adbe5d28a992d486a4b216acde1846dbc75","tid":1911814,"uid":43066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7de86e8bec4b43d1bf287b918971925e405dbe51","tid":1911814,"uid":43066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi